fields.name: Abilities:
fields.value:
- Bat Eyelashes (Night): Entrance target player with your eyes into revealing their class type.
> - Can't target King
- Dark Wisp (Night, 2 Uses): Uncage a dark wisp, making the Unseen appear not suspicious tonight.

fields.name: Attributes:
fields.value:
- Royal Blood: During elections for a new King, votes for you count twice.
> - Passive kept on class change.
